author: skitching
msg: * Initialise logical parent link in a second pass. This is needed to solve the case where a component class extends a generated component in the same project (eg the Div component in Tomahawk, which extends HtmlTag, which is generated from AbstractHtmlTag).
* Ensure modelId property is set on everything. The generated file has a mix of entities from the current project and imported ones, and we need to be able to tell them apart sometimes.
* Improve unit tests to output better diagnostic info
